nodes.text: Aidan Cook is an English puppeteer and actor who worked as a creature and droid performer for Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, Rogue One: A Star Wars Story and Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi. His characters include Bobbajo, Edrio, Caitken, Strono Tuggs and Benthic.
